cat.gencat.ctti.canigo.arch.security.provider.saml

Class SAMLAuthenticationWithMemberProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • cat.gencat.ctti.canigo.arch.security.provider.saml.SAMLAuthenticationWithMemberProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean, org.springframework.context.MessageSourceAware, org.springframework.core.Ordered, org.springframework.security.authentication.AuthenticationProvider

    @Component
 @Named(value="samlAuthenticationWithMemberProvider")
public class SAMLAuthenticationWithMemberProvider
extends Object
    Does not extend from AbstractUserDetailsAuthenticationProvider as this class supports a different authentication token based on SAML assertion as the sole credentials needed to authenticate the user. To be configured in /src/main/resources/spring/app-custom-security.xml com <security:authentication-provider ref= "samlAuthenticationWithMemberProvider" />
    Author:
    cscanigo
